dmca.title: RE TM Request NobleCountyFreecycle(IN)
dmca.body:
Attention: Deron Beal, Executive Director, Freecycle(TM)
cc:  Freecycle(TM) group owner


Hi Deron,
 
We haven't heard from these owners at all.  We sent a TM Request letter about 10 days ago and asked for a reply.  It looks like a headless group.  Should I go ahead and remove them from freecycle.org and set up a new local group?  Or do you want to try to contact them first?  I am honestly hoping they see this and contact me, but we can't be sure that they will.
 
Thank you,
 
Jeanette
Freecycle(TM) Trademark Representative
trademark1@freecycle.org
